commit.message:
Merge pull request #11 from hobarrera/style-tweaks

Style tweaks

Merge pull request #12 from hobarrera/default-root-logger

Operate on the default logger by default

Catch Exception, rather than blind-catch

This prevent catching things that we generally don't want to catch
memory error, SystemExit, etc.

Operate on the default logger by default

`basic_config` operates on the default logger by default. Implement the
same behaviour for `simple_verbosity_option`, so that both can be called
with no arguments when the root logger should be used.
Accept string in place of logger
